{"tid":2070551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"七學警實務練習時違守則　警方：正被紀律調查","createTime":"2020-06-19T07:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T12:35:54.000Z","uid":212626,"like":27,"dislike":180,"uniUserReply":121,"replies":[{"pid":"99da8fc9de2fe64c0bb24f2abcd4ec2d7e9104e4","tid":2070551,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"有傳媒報道指，七名學警上月在警察學院一次筆試中集體以「貓紙」作弊，被口頭訓斥後仍獲准畢業。警方回應指得悉事件，初步了解相信七名學警在今年五月，出席實務練習時違反守則，其後已經重做練習並成功通過，涉事七人正被紀律調查，不會與其他同班學警一同結業。<br />\n<br />\n警方強調，警察學院訓練嚴謹，參與課程的學警須接受多方面訓練並通過最後考試，表現達標才能結業，重申警方重視人員的操守，調查後如發現有任何違法行為，會嚴肅處理。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1314034&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1314034%26csid%3D261_341&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=6c909b00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1314034&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"6e3209f9836ce4c6dab547464c7366f635abe816","tid":2070551,"uid":50457,"like":183,"dislike":1,"score":182,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:58:37.000Z","msg":"警方重視人員的操守<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d181944ca463179c70cfc7b6616f8397e9e5e211","tid":2070551,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60951280bbc1bc82cae38f27a8268d8658f4c68a","tid":2070551,"uid":80724,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:01:26.000Z","msg":"過幾日，已訓斥"},{"pid":"16a442d5a09f40c06ac0b680fff240f90f48a663","tid":2070551,"uid":173060,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"